The PUK code for mobile number $mpn is : $puk
</div>
<div>
To unlock your mobile enter your PUK code using the instructions detailed in your mobile phone user guide.
Customers using Motorola handsets should key **05* then wait until prompted before entering your PUK code.
For Panasonic handsets you must follow the PUK code with #.
Please note, incorrectly entering the PUK code more than 10 times will disable your SIM and you will require a replacement.
If you experience difficulty with your PUK code or require further assistance please contact Customer Services.
